00:25.979 --> 00:29.367
And they have to answer the question. Then if they answer the question, you go, "OK, go ahead."

00:31.555 --> 00:37.380
I mean obviously, kids like grown-ups, sadly, are very amused by body function...

00:37.999 --> 00:39.376
...references of any kind.

