01:03.005 --> 01:06.918
...it's gonna get a big laugh, you know. And of course they fell over, you know.

01:07.839 --> 01:09.457
What is the game called "Fly Over the Bath"?

01:10.070 --> 01:11.138
"Fly Over the Bath" is...

01:12.033 --> 01:15.275
...one kid is in the bath and he has a little squeeze toy that fills,...

01:15.382 --> 01:16.531
