01:16.659 --> 01:19.451
...and the other kid, I fly them over the bath.

01:19.545 --> 01:22.580
And as the one kid flies over, the kid in the bath squirts...

01:22.963 --> 01:24.117
...the other kid in the face...

01:24.718 --> 01:25.329
