01:39.122 --> 01:42.054
And I tell the one lying on the bed, "In one minute..."

01:42.166 --> 01:46.589
"...you're gonna see a little kid dressed in pink, is gonna come flying right over your face."

01:46.737 --> 01:47.795
"So just watch out for that."

01:51.190 --> 01:53.603
